summary:
Hello! I'm a Creative Technology student at the University of Twente from Singapore looking to pursue a career as a Unity Developer or Software Engineer in the next stage of my life. I am actively developing games on Unity but have also worked on art exhibitions that were displayed at the GOGBOT festival in Enschede and TEC ART festival in Rotterdam. My main interests are in programming (C#) with further experience developing in C++, C, and Java (Processing) in the past.

On the side, I'm a Musician and Audio Engineer with several released works. I also have experience working in a post audio house recording VO talents and vocalists and working on commercials.
